import { Box, Button, FormControl, FormLabel, Heading, Input } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import SidebarSuperAdmin from "../../components/SidebarSuperAdmin";

const FishData = () => {
    return(
        <>
            <Box bgColor={"#F5F7FA"} bgSize={"cover"} height={"100vh"} display={"flex"}>
                <SidebarSuperAdmin/>

                <Box margin={"50px"} width={"7xl"} display={"flex"} flexDirection={"column"} marginLeft={"280px"}>
                    <Box marginLeft={"10px"} marginTop={"20px"} >
                        <Heading>Fish Data</Heading>
                    </Box>

                    <Box padding={"30px"} bgColor={"#FFFFFF"} borderRadius={"30px"} marginTop={"30px"} minHeight={"75vh"}>
                        <Button marginLeft={"80%"}>+ Add</Button>
                    </Box>
                </Box>
            </Box>

            {/* <FormControl isRequired width={"100%"}>
                <Box width={"40%"}>
                <FormLabel>Id</FormLabel>
                <Input placeholder="id" type="text" marginBottom={"20px"}></Input>

                <FormLabel>Name</FormLabel>
                <Input placeholder="fish name" type="text" marginBottom={"20px"}></Input>

                <FormLabel>Minimal Price</FormLabel>
                <Input placeholder="min price /kg" type="number" marginBottom={"20px"}></Input>

                <FormLabel>Maximal Price</FormLabel>
                <Input placeholder="max price /kg" type="number" marginBottom={"20px"}></Input>
                </Box>
                </FormControl> */}
        </>
    )
}

export default FishData;
